    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《复原》运用了魔方的基本概念，但其侧重于现实生活中的物体，给玩家带来更舒缓的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏方式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拼图以各种组合出现；你需要通过旋转、平移或缩放来找到每一块拼图的正确位置，直到组合出物体的原始形状。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/fd0f6c60344441692a7f66ca5e648f19.poster.avif?t=1763534464\" width=426 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/fd0f6c60344441692a7f66ca5e648f19.webm?t=1763534464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/fd0f6c60344441692a7f66ca5e648f19.mp4?t=1763534464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>操作方式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/2bf79e0356c3ff857ea3e5b20c306109.poster.avif?t=1763534464\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/2bf79e0356c3ff857ea3e5b20c306109.webm?t=1763534464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/2bf79e0356c3ff857ea3e5b20c306109.mp4?t=1763534464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 点击每块拼图，将其选中 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 单击形状外部以选择整个拼图并更改视角 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在形状外部点击可以选择整个拼图并改变视角。按住左键，单击并将鼠标向左或向右移动，可根据形状的动作进行旋转、平移或缩放。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如同在现实生活中一样，神秘世界被困在扭蛋机中等待释放，通过解决谜题，你可以获得游戏内的硬币，这些硬币可以在扭蛋机上进行消费以释放下一个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/642d04b137ef615c65570039382e149f.poster.avif?t=1763534464\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/642d04b137ef615c65570039382e149f.webm?t=1763534464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1853410/extras/642d04b137ef615c65570039382e149f.mp4?t=1763534464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 轻松无压力，没有计时设置；你只需保持淡定，跟着自己的节奏即可。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 操作简单：拿起&amp;放下。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过修改天气以及时间来调整房间的舒适度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 单手操作即可（另一只手可以用来喝饮料！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 令人愉悦的音效和氛围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 舒缓的原创背景音乐。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 适用于社区和流媒体传播！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 体验可爱的主题世界！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 没有任何惩罚机制，生活本身已经够不容易了！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 韩语, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 加泰罗尼亚语, 繁体中文",
